Dependencies:
    The external Python packages this project depends on
    are listed below.

    nltk
    numpy
    scipy
    pandas
    scikit-learn
    gensim
    Cython
    BeautifulSoup

    To install, ensure pip is available. This can be determined
    by running `which pip3`.  If there is no output, please run
    `sudo apt install python3-pip`.

    Once pip has been installed, all of the above packages can
    be downloaded and installed at once using the command below:

        pip3 install nltk pandas scikit-learn Cython gensim BeautifulSoup

    An install script has been included for convenience.